{"id": 2122, "genre": 1000, "title": "你见过哪些在“公开发表意见”时的跑偏类型？", "description": "那些常常把讨论环境带坏的人还有多少，请回忆在留言区", "record_count": 6591, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180122181226QKaSgiG02x5fVLMu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-22T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3579, "title": "你见过哪些在“公开发表意见”时的跑偏类型？", "content": "你见过哪些在“公开发表意见”时的跑偏类型?", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 259329, "content": "这没意义型，“懂的人不说也懂，不懂的人说了也不懂”", "image": "img/option/option/20180115174831UcdlpogIvRNeCiVX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259332, "content": "瞎总结型，“从评论区的留言就能看出我国青年xxx”", "image": "img/option/option/20180115174930fGuSn3ejWsy0mPJZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259333, "content": "反正我对型，只要和我意见不同的都有错", "image": "img/option/option/201801151750426v1UgIMuwa0n5Qyi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259335, "content": "都不容易型，“就算了吧”", "image": "img/option/option/20180115175257syTeNuWUIFdS5o2x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259321, "content": "这是常识型，单方面把某些观点视为理所当然", "image": "img/option/option/20180115173825tdCqbz4RXv3PnwTQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259322, "content": "以偏概全型，“俄罗斯人都xx”、“INTJ的人都这样”", "image": "img/option/option/20180115174021Gi8EH24V3Mn0eWNU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259324, "content": "就事论人型，把重点放在当事人出身、人品、教育上", "image": "img/option/option/20180115174408ruPxhi2OY5Isay0n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259325, "content": "锄强扶弱型，帮弱不帮理，以一切“被删”为荣", "image": "img/option/option/20180115174720cJiHkomUvRzFlSBd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}